    { "stepId": 3, "title": "结论", "content": "由 \\(M=g_0R^2/G\\) 和 \\(\\rho=3M/(4\\pi R^3)\\)，得 \\(\\rho=\\dfrac{3\\pi g_0}{GT^2(g_0-g)}\\)，故选 B。", "knowledge": ["密度"], "commonMistakes": [] }
